Never heard of DeepSeek?This model is about the same as gpt-4o-mini, cheaper and faster.Minecraft fine-tuning gpt-4o-mini v4 full body Trained for Chinese to English translation,But there are still some flaws that need to be fine-tuned.
uploadForm.title: JSON Translation Tool
uploadForm.emailContact: Email me at h{'@'}lvjia.cc if you need it
uploadForm.loadingText: If you're stuck at a certain value for half a day with no translation progress, wait more, don't refresh, because the upstream load is full and it may recover in 1 minute or so. It's also possible that no one has used the model you chose in the last 24 hours, OpenAI's servers need at least 6 seconds to start the model.
uploadForm.description: Upload a JSON file to be auto-translated to Chinese. Please make sure to select a non-nested JSON file. Choose a translation method before uploading, defaults to English to Chinese.
uploadForm.privacyDesc: We collect only anonymous access statistics, no personal information

uploadForm.thankYou: Thank you for your support! Your ID is:
uploadForm.tutorialContent1: Download a compression tool like 7-zip, right-click jar to open or extract, and find the assets folder for the mod's resource files.
uploadForm.tutorialContent4: If you unzipped it, rezip it as a normal zip, ensuring the top-level directory is not a single folder, and you probably zipped it successfully, rename it to jar.
uploadForm.tutorialContent2: In the assets folder, there will be a non-Minecraft named folder. Open it, and the json files inside are the language files.
uploadForm.privacyModalContent: Counts real users, and doesn't share with any third parties.
uploadForm.tutorialContent3: Upload it here, save it after translating, rename it to zh_cn.json, and drag it in.
